.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-LISTFORWARDS-IN-MSAT-RANGE" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-listforwards-in-msat-range \- FEAT-2789 node-listforwards-in-msat-range
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-listforwards-in-msat-range
.SH DESCRIPTION
Reports the range (max minus min) of incoming msat values across settled forwards (FEAT-2789).
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN with key \fBin_msat_range\fR.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
